    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You spit out a large quantity of sticky liquid that covers the area. Creatures within the area cannot run or charge, and move at half their speed during their turn. They also suffer a -2 penalty to Defense and Reflex saves. Characters that use the Tadayou technique before moving through the area remain unaffected</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to increase the Cost to 6 and increase the area to a 15 ft square.<br><br>The fifth step allows you to increase the Cost to 8 and increase the area to a 20 ft square.</p>\n",
